    Included missling packages for python3
    1. dpkt - dpkt_fix is an outdated package written for Python 2, The dpkt_fix package was a temporary,
    unofficial fork created years ago to fix a specific bug in version 1.7 of dpkt. Since then,
    the official dpkt package has been heavily updated, fully supports Python 3, and includes all
    those old fixes
    
    2. pyarrow - While Pandas comes with standard CSV support out of the box, it requires an extra library
    called pyarrow to handle Feather files.

